snippet.title: Jon and Sibty English Learning Lesson 41 (Intermediate) (Thai) (Thailand)
snippet.description:
Jon and Sibty English Learning

Add Sibty on Instagram 
https://www.instagram.com/nuttha_noottala/

In this show the student will learn English with me over 1 year showing the progress each day. We will use games and exercises to learn English correctly without the grammar mistakes that are taught in schools. 

Teaching experience:
5 years teaching experience. TESOL 120 hours certified. Classroom English as well as one on one. 5,000+ students. 

Equipment:
GoPro Hero 7 Black
Rode smartLav+
Cyberlink PowerDirector 18
